\v 10 \x - \xo 6:10 \xt Hip 10:32-34\x*Kumwes…ôn ko r…®pkenouenou mh…ô narimnari me s…ôm…ôme hi…ôno t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô noien s…ôv…ônhi ratukwatukw a ia n…ôp…®n me pam. N…ôn…ô in ko r…®pko mh…ô n…ôri au…ôr a ia noien amasan s…ôv…ôi nokeikeiien s…ô hi…ôno min, n…ôn…ô mamho ihi, n…ôp…®n hi…ônasitu ia n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ônhi.
\v 11 \x - \xo 6:11 \xt Hip 3:14\x*N…ôn…ô k…®maha iahokeikei m…ô k…®miaha kuatia kuatia rer…®miaha tra…°ien t…® noien iam…®nha ir…ô mamh…ôuv…ôn meste tih…ôuvehi n…ôfe hiam…ômri pen …ôknek…®n n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®miaha ir…ô.
\v 12 K…®maha iah…ôpw…ôh nokeikeiien m…ô tiharpaha, m…ôt…ô iahokeikei m…ô tih…ômwhen ia n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme hamahat…ôt…ô, n…ôn…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônraha r…ôpw…ômw…®s, n…ôn…ô h…ôukur…ôn nuvehiien narimnari me s…ôm…ôme Kumwes…ôn r…®no promes m…ô truvei pen m…®nraha.
\s1 Promes s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn tram…ôkeikei muvehe muku…ô
\p 
\v 13 N…ôp…®n Kumwes…ôn r…®no promes m Epraham fwe kupw…ôn, naha…° riti mwi riw…ôn m…ô in truvehi mo n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônhi r…®pam, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ô…°hi Kumwes…ôn rasori m…ôpi raka naha…° me pam. Ro pen Kumwes…ôn ruvehi atukw a kw…ôsuahi ia n…ô…°h…®n,
\v 14 \x - \xo 6:14 \xt Jen 22:16-17\x*mani m…ô, ‚ÄúIakani n…®p…ôrhienien m…ô iou tak…ôkwein amasan ia niram, mo n…ôrmama ia kw…ôn…ôkwus s…ôim tuh…ôp…®k.‚Äù
\v 15 T…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ôi Epraham r…ôpw…ômw…®s, in reitenhi meste ruvehi narimnari me n…ôha Kumwes…ôn r…®no promes m…ô truvei pen min.
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 6:16 \xt Eks 22:10-11\x*N…ôp…®n i…ôrmama ruvehi kw…ôsuahi ia n…ô…°hi i…ôm…ô asori riti s…ôv…ônhi, n…ôn…ô kw…ôsuahi n…ôha s…ôv…ônhi r…ôrihi n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônhi r…®pam. N…ôn…ô n…ôrmama tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ia n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônhi, ko h…ôpk…ôvis…ô mh…ô mwi tukwe.
\v 17 Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvehi kw…ôsuahi ia n…ô…°h…®n iam…®nhi ir…ô, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in rokeikei m…ô tro n…ôrmama me i s…ôm…ôme tuh…ôuvehi n…ôfe in r…®no promes h…ôukur…ôn amasan m…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônhi ko k…®pkuvsini mh…ô n…ôp…®n riti.
\v 18 \x - \xo 6:18 \xt Nam 23:19, 1Saml 15:29\x*N…ô…°kiariien mi n…ôha promes m…®ne kw…ôsuahi ko kr…®pkuvsini mh…ô ia n…ôp…®n riti. Ia n…ô…°kiariien mi n…ôha Kumwes…ôn ko r…®pkeiku…ô mh…ô. K…®taha n…ôrmama me i s…ônap raka mh…ôuv…ôn mamh…ôrkwaf…ô ipaka t…® Kumwes…ôn, n…ô…°kiariien mi n…ôha krouasitu asori ia k…®taha, rauo m…ô k…®taha ts…ôkwt…ômhiri …ôknek…®n noien i samo, noien s…ô sameitenhi n…ôri amasan i Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ômri kupw…ôn ia k…®taha.
\v 19 N…ôri amasan n…ôha sameitenhi ram…ôkwt…ômhiri n…®m…®ruien s…ôk…®taha r…ômwhen ia aean s…ô ravi t…ôrini n…®t…ôt…ô. K…®taha sameitenhi n…ôri amasan n…ôha r…ômwhen m…ô k…®taha s…ôuv…ôuvnimw…ô raka ia kwopun ikinan anan s…ô t…®nari ramo tukuaha…° fwe ia neiai ia nimw…ô s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn.
\v 20 \x - \xo 6:20 \xt Lev 16:2-3, Lev 16:12,15, Hip 5:6\x*Iesu ruv…ôuvnimw…ô raka ia kwopun n…ôha. In ruvnimw…ô tukwini s…ôk…®taha m…ô tr…ôsev…ôr ia suatuk s…ôk…®taha. In ruv…ôuvehe raka m…®no pris asori anan ir…ô r…ômwhen ia Melkisetek fwe kupw…ôn, n…ôn…ô in trauvehi ia n…ôp…®n me ia nuk nuk me.
\c 7
\s1 Pris asori anan n…ôha Melkisetek
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 7:1 \xt Jen 14:17-20\x*Fwe kupw…ôn, i…ôm…ô i Melkisetek, in ki…° s…ôv…ôi Salem, n…ôn…ô in pris s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn i in rasori p…®k anan. N…ôp…®n Epraham r…®mav…ôn ia narua…°…ônien ir…ôha ki…° me, n…ôn…ô in ruvehi irapw ir…ôha, n…ôn…ô in r…®r…ôr…®…° m…®nauvehe, Melkisetek ramev…ôn m…ôtoni ia suatuk, n…ôn…ô r…ôfwaki m…ôres Kumwes…ôn m…ô tr…ôkwein amasan ia Epraham.
\v 2 N…ôn…ô Epraham roueite naut…ô me pam ia kusen ten n…ôn…ô muvei pen kusen kuatia m Melkisetek. Naha…° i Melkisetek n…®pwran i m…ô Ki…° s…ôv…ôi Natukwatukwien. N…ôn…ô n…ô…°h…®n riti mwi kam…ôkwein in ir…ô m…ô ki…° s…ôv…ôi Salem. N…®pwran m…ô Ki…° s…ôv…ôi N…ôm…ôrinuien.
\v 3 \x - \xo 7:3 \xt Sam 110:4\x*N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan r…®pk…ô…°kiari mh…ô ia tata s…ôv…ônhi m…®ne mama s…ôv…ônhi m…®ne kw…ôn…ôkwus me s…ôv…ônhi, n…ôn…ô m…®pk…®ni mh…ô n…ôp…®n r…®n…ôtui ir…ô m…®ne n…ôp…®n r…®mamh…ô ir…ô. R…ômwhen m…ô in r…®pkemh…ô mh…ô, in ramo ihi wok s…ôv…ôi pris. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô ik…ôtoni m…ô in r…ômwhen ia T…®ni Kumwes…ôn, in pris rer…®n riti.
\p 
\v 4 Rer…®miaha tr…®rhi ro Melkisetek m…ô in n…ôfe i…ôm…ô asori. Epraham kaha kupw…ôn s…ôk…®taha r…®noeite naut…ô me s…ôv…ôi ki…° me s…ôm…ôme r…®m…ôuvehi irapw ir…ôha ia narua…°…ônien, muai ia kusen ten muvei pen kusen kuatia m Melkisetek.
\v 5 \x - \xo 7:5 \xt Nam 18:21\x*K…®taha s…ôukur…ôn m…ô ia nuk me pam n…ôkur Isrel tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôuai naut…ô me s…ôv…ônraha ia kusen ten mh…ôuvei pen kusen kuatia m kw…ôn…ôkwus me s…ôv…ôi Livae s…ôm…ôme ir…ôha pris me r…ômwhen ia Loa s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn rani. N…ôri au…ôr a m…ô pris me n…ôha ir…ôha kw…ôn…ôkwus me s…ôv…ôi Epraham, m…ôt…ô pi…ôvnraha me tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôuvei pen naut…ô me n…ôha m…®nraha.
\v 6 Melkisetek, r…®pko mh…ô in kw…ôn…ôkwus riti s…ôv…ôi Livae, m…ôt…ô Epraham r…®m…ôuai naut…ô me n…ôha ia kusen ten muvei pen kuatia min. N…ôn…ô Melkisetek r…ôfwaki m Kumwes…ôn m…ô tr…ôkwein amasan ia Epraham i Kumwes…ôn r…®no promes me min.
\v 7 N…ôn…ô n…ôrmama pam h…ôukur…ôn. I…ôrmama s…ô rauvehi naha…° asori tr…ôfwaki m…ô Kumwes…ôn tr…ôkwein amasan ia i…ôrmama s…ô in inh…ôr…®pw ir…ô.
\v 8 N…ôn…ô pris me i ipwet m…®ne s…ôm…ôme kauai naut…ô me kusen ten kauvei pen kuatia m…®nraha, ir…ôha n…ôrmama me a s…ôm…ôme tuh…ôpkemh…ô. M…ôt…ô Melkisetek i kuai naut…ô me kusen ten kuvei pen kuatia min, N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan rani m…ô in ram…®ru.
\v 9 Rosi k…®taha s…ôukur…ôn n…®niien m…ô Livae, i…ôm…ô i n…ôkur Isrel ipwet m…®ne kamh…ôuai naut…ô me s…ôv…ônraha kusen ten mamh…ôuvei pen kusen kuatia m kw…ôn…ôkwus me s…ôv…ônhi, r…ômwhen m…ô Livae atukwatukw n…ôha fwe kupw…ôn r…®m…ôuai naut…ô n…ôha s…ôv…ôi Epraham kusen ten muvei pen m Melkisetek.
\v 10 Iakani iam…®nha ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…®p…ôrhienien Livae r…®n…ôpw…ôh ihi n…ôtuiien ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha Melkisetek r…®n…ôtoni Epraham ia suatuk, m…ôt…ô in r…®n…ômak raka ia n…®te\f + \fr 7:10 \ft U…ô ‚Äúin fwe ia n…®pwrai kaha s…ôv…ônhi‚Äù\f* kaha n…ôha s…ôv…ônhi Epraham.
\s1 Iesu Kristo in r…ômwhen ia Melkisetek
\p 
\v 11 Wok s…ôv…ôi pris me n…ôha kamh…ôuku pen ia kw…ôn…ôkwus s…ôv…ôi Livae in nukune Loa s…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvei pen m n…ôkur Isrel. M…ôt…ô wok s…ôv…ôi pris me n…ôha r…ôpw…ôh n…ômwhenien, ko ir…ôha h…ôpk…ômri atukwatukw pam mh…ô nari. Ro pen pris …ôp…ô riti tram…ôkeikei muvehe, m…®pk…ômwhen mh…ô ia Eron, m…ôt…ô in r…ômwhen ia Melkisetek.
\v 12 N…ôn…ô hi…ôukur…ôn n…ôp…®n kuvsini noien s…ôv…ôi n…®rfiien pris, n…ôn…ô tukam…ôkeikei kuvsini mwi Loa.
\v 13 Tram…ôkeikei mo iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô k…®taha sam…ô…°kiari ia I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha s…ô r…®m…ôuku pen ia kw…ôn…ôkwus …ôp…ô riti. I…ôrmama riti riw…ôn ia kw…ôn…ôkwus n…ôha r…®no raka wok s…ôv…ôi pris ia n…®fat…ô.
\v 14 \x - \xo 7:14 \xt Jen 49:10, Aes 11:1, Mat 2:6, Rev 5:5\x*N…ôrmama h…ôuv…ôukur…ôn raka m…ô in r…®m…ôuku pen ia kw…ôn…ôkwus s…ôv…ôi Juta. N…ôp…®n Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses ram…ô…°kiari ia wok s…ôv…ôi pris me, r…®pk…ô…°kiari anan mh…ô ia kw…ôn…ôkwus n…ôha.
\v 15 Ruvehe mo mwi nukur…ônien ir…ô m…ô kuvsini noien s…ôv…ôi n…®rfiien pris t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô pris riti mwi ruv…ôuvehe raka in r…ômwhen ia Melkisetek.
\v 16 In r…®m…ôuvehe pris m…®pkesi pen mh…ô loa n…ôha s…ô rani kw…ôn…ôkwus s…ôv…ôi pris me, m…ôt…ô resi pen n…®skaiien s…ôv…ôi n…®m…®ruien i ko r…®pkiw…ôn mh…ô ia n…ôp…®n riti.
\v 17 \x - \xo 7:17 \xt Hip 5:6\x*Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan ram…ô…°kiari ir…ô, mam…®ni m…ô,
\q1 ‚ÄúIk pris riti r…ômwhen ia Melkisetek fwe kupw…ôn,
\q2 n…ôn…ô tiko wok s…ôv…ôi pris ia n…ôp…®n me ia nuk nuk me.‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 N…ô…°kiariien n…ôha r…®n…ômri karen loa kupw…ôn, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…®skaiien s…ôv…ônhi riw…ôn, in r…®pkasitu mh…ô, ko r…®pko mh…ô nari riti.
\v 19 \x - \xo 7:19 \xt Hip 9:9\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Loa s…ôv…ôi Moses r…®reirei n…ômri atukwatukwien nari riti. N…ôn…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni n…ôha, noien …ôp…ô riti s…ô in ramasan m…ôpi raka ruv…ôuvehi t…ômwhek…®n m…ô k…®taha ts…ômri pen …ôknek…®n n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®taha ir…ô. Noien n…ôha in suatuk s…ôk…®taha t…® nev…ônien ipaka t…® Kumwes…ôn.
\p 
\v 20 Nari riti mwi Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvehi kw…ôsuahi muvehi ut…ô noien n…ôha. N…ôp…®n n…ôrmama me n…ôha fwe kupw…ôn h…ôuvehe mho ir…ôha pris me, nuvehiien kw…ôsuahi riw…ôn.
\v 21 \x - \xo 7:21 \xt Hip 5:6\x*M…ôt…ô n…ôp…®n Iesu r…®m…ôuvehe mo in pris, Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvehi kw…ôsuahi m…®ni m…ô:
\q1 ‚ÄúI…ôr…®m…ônu r…®m…ôuvehi kw…ôsuahi riti,
\q2 n…ôn…ô ko r…®pk…ôrari mh…ô mwi ia n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônhi.
\q1 Ik tiko wok s…ôv…ôi pris ia n…ôp…®n me ia nuk nuk me.‚Äù
\m 
\v 22 \x - \xo 7:22 \xt Hip 8:6, 12:24\x*Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvehi kw…ôsuahi iam…®nhi ir…ô, mo Iesu ruvehe i…ôrmama s…ô r…ômri n…ô…°kiariien i k…®n…ôrihi t…ôrini …ôknek…®n ir…ô ramasan m…ôpi raka.
\p 
\v 23 Nari riti mwi, pris kupw…ôn me h…ôp…®k, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô kuatia tro wok mamev…ôn memh…ô n…ôn…ô riti ruvehi t…ômwhek…®n. Ir…ôha h…ôpkuvehi mh…ô wok r…ôpw…ômw…®s.
\v 24 M…ôt…ô Iesu, in truvehi wok s…ôv…ôi pris ia nuk nuk me m…®pko mh…ô sampam, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in ramar…ô rer…®n.
\v 25 \fig N…®fat…ô kauvani n…®pwrai n…ôrim…®ru me ir…ô kauvei pen m Kumwes…ôn|alt="Altar of burnt offerin…°" src="HK00256B.TIF" size="span" loc="same pa…°e as verse" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="Hip 7:25"\fig*\x - \xo 7:25 \xt Rom 8:34\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô in rukur…ôn nuvehim…®ruien n…ôrmama me s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôuv…ôn t…® Kumwes…ôn ia suatuk s…ô in r…®no. In rukur…ôn nuvehim…®ruien ir…ôha ia nuk nuk me m…®pko mh…ô sampam t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in ramar…ô rer…®n, mam…ô…°kiari tukwini s…ôv…ônraha m Kumwes…ôn.
\p 
\v 26 \x - \xo 7:26 \xt Hip 3:1\x*Pris asori anan riti s…ô ro iam…®nhi in r…ômwhen t…® nasituien ia k…®taha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in i…ôm…ô ikinan, in r…®pko mh…ô noien …ôr…ôha u…ô noien …ômkem…®k. In rop…ô ia n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamho noien …ôr…ôha, n…ôn…ô k…®m…ôuvehi ut…ô in, in rasori m…ôpi raka ir…ôha fwe ia neiai.
\v 27 \x - \xo 7:27 \xt Hip 5:3\x*In rop…ô ia pris asori anan me n…ôha. N…ôp…®n me pam ir…ôha tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôkupw…ôn mh…ôvi net…ô t…® naikuas rakaien ia noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônraha kurir…ô h…ôpko s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama t…® naikuas rakaien noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônraha. M…ôt…ô Iesu r…®m…ôvi net…ô m kuatia a r…®n…ômwhen ko r…®pko mh…ô mwi ia n…ôp…®n riti mwi. In r…®no noien n…ôha n…ôp…®n r…®n…ôseni n…®m…®ruien s…ôv…ônhi memh…ô.
\v 28 \x - \xo 7:28 \xt Hip 5:1-2\x*Loa rauvehi ut…ô pris asori anan me s…ôm…ôme h…ôpk…®skai mh…ô. M…ôt…ô kw…ôsuahi s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn, s…ô rukurir…ô ia Loa, in ruvehi ut…ô T…®ni s…ô ramasan m…ômwhen t…® noien wok n…ôha ia nuk nuk me m…®pko mh…ô sampam.
\c 8
\s1 Iesu in pris asori anan s…ôk…®taha
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 8:1 \xt Hip 1:3, 3:1, Hip 10:12, 12:2\x*K…®maha iaham…ô…°kiari ia n…ôri i, m…ôt…ô nukunen ro iam…®nhi ir…ô. S…ôk…®taha riti pris asori anan r…ômwhen a ia s…ô i iaham…ôni. In fwe ia neiai. Jea n…ôha Kumwes…ôn asori ram…ôkure ir…ô mam…ôr…®m…ônu, pris asori anan n…ôha s…ôk…®taha r…®n…ôkure ia n…®kare jea n…ôha mwatuk.
\v 2 In ramo wok ia n…ôkwai kwopun ikinan, in i nimw…ô tapolen p…ôrhien s…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôvi fwe ia neiai. R…®pko mh…ô i…ôrmama r…®m…ôvi nimw…ô tapolen n…ôha.
\p 
\v 3 Pris asori anan me pam s…ôm…ôme Loa r…®m…ôuvehi ut…ô ir…ôha wok s…ôv…ônraha fwe ik…®n. Ir…ôha ham…ôuvei pen narimnari me m Kumwes…ôn, mamh…ôvi net…ô ia n…®fat…ô s…ôv…ônhi. Ia suatuk kuatia a, pris asori anan s…ôk…®taha, in mwi tram…ôkeikei muvei pen nari riti m Kumwes…ôn.
\v 4 Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô in ramar…ô ihi ia t…®pr…ôn…ô i, ko r…®pkuvehe mh…ô mo in pris riti, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô pris me h…ônar…ô raka m…ô tuh…ôuvei pen narimnari m Kumwes…ôn r…ômwhen Loa rani.
\v 5 \x - \xo 8:5 \xt Kol 2:17, Hip 9:23, Eks 25:40\x*Pris me n…ôha, ir…ôha kamho wok s…ôv…ônraha ia n…ôkwai nimw…ô s…ô rauvnhi a narimnari me s…ôm…ôme kamhar…ô ia neiai. Ro pen n…ôp…®n Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôni pen t…® Moses fwe kupw…ôn m…ô tr…®vi nimw…ô tapolen, m…®ni m…ô,
\q1 ‚ÄúTikam…ôkeikei m…ôtui amasan m…ô tiko narimnari me i s…ôv…ôi nimw…ô tapolen
\q2 resi pen atukwatukw n…ôfe iak…®nahat…ôn raka ik ir…ô fwe ia t…ôku…ôr.‚Äù
\m 
\v 6 \x - \xo 8:6 \xt Hip 7:22; 9:15; 12:24\x*M…ôt…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni Kristo r…®m…ôuvehi wok s…ôv…ôi pris s…ô ramasan m…ôpi raka wok s…ôv…ôi pris kupw…ôn me. R…ômwhen a mwi n…ô…°kiariien s…ô in r…®n…ôrihi t…ôrini …ôknek…®n ramasan m…ôpi raka n…ô…°kiariien kupw…ôn, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô ram…ôrer ut…ô ia promes me s…ôm…ôme hamasan mh…ôpi raka.
\p 
\v 7 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô k…®m…ôkupw…ôn k…ôrihi t…ôrini …ôknek…®n r…®pkatukwatukw pam mh…ô. Ko ratukwatukw pam tuk…ôrihi t…ôrini …ôknek…®n n…ô…°kiariien vi riti t…® n…ôfe?
\v 8 M…ôt…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ôtoni m…ô ir…ôha h…ôpkatukwatukw mh…ô n…ôp…®n rani m…ô,
\q1 ‚ÄúN…ôp…®n n…ôha ik…®n rauvehe
\q2 s…ô tak…ôrihi t…ôrini …ôknek…®n n…ô…°kiariien vi riti
\q1 n…ôkur Isrel m…®ne n…ôkur Juta tuhar…ô ir…ô. \fig Nimw…ô tapolen s…ô n…ôkur Isrel h…ônam…ôfwaki ik…®n ia n…ôp…®n s…ôv…ôi Oltestamen|alt="Dia…°ram of the Tabernacle in the wilderness, listin…° parts" src="TabernacleDiagramKTM.tif" size="span" loc="full width after 8.5" copy="2013 SIL - Art by Gordon Thompson" ref="Heb 8:5"\fig*
\q1 
\v 9 N…ô…°kiariien n…ôha r…®pk…ômhwen mh…ô ia n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha iak…®n…ôrihi t…ôrini …ôknek…®n
\q2 m…ô kaha me s…ôv…ônraha tuhar…ô ir…ô,
\q1 ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha iak…®m…ôuvehi r…ô…°…®nraha
\q2 miri irapw ir…ôha fwe t…ôn…ô Ijip.
\q1 Ir…ôha h…ôpk…ôkwt…ômhiri mh…ô n…ô…°kiariien s…ôiou,
\q2 n…ôn…ô ro pen iakenouenou ir…ôha. Iou I…ôr…®m…ônu iakani iam…®nha ir…ô.
\q1 
\v 10 \x - \xo 8:10 \xt Hip 10:16\x*N…ôn…ô iou I…ôr…®m…ônu iakani m…ô n…ô…°kiariien s…ôiou tak…ôrihi t…ôrini …ôknek…®n ia n…ôp…®n s…ô truvehe n…ôkur Isrel tuhar…ô ir…ô ro iam…®nhi ir…ô:
