\v 1 \x - \xo 10:1 \xt Hip 8:5\x*Narimnari me s…ôv…ôi Loa h…ômwhen a ia n…ôn…®mwi nari m nari amasan me s…ôm…ôme tr…®pko mh…ô tui h…ôuvehe, r…®pko mh…ô n…®pwrai narimnari me. Ia nuk me pam pris me n…ôha s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Isrel kamho a nari kuatia, mamh…ôvi net…ô t…® noien …ôr…ôha. M…ôt…ô n…®te n…ôrim…®ru me n…ôha r…®reirei noien n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôuvehe t…® Kumwes…ôn hatukwatukw ia n…ônimen.
