\v 8 Ia n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha ir…ônh…ô, Kristo r…®m…ôkupw…ôn m…®ni m…ô, ‚ÄúIk ik…ôpw…ôh nokeikeiien noien n…ôha kamousi …ôpune n…ôrim…®ru me kauvei pehe mik, u…ô noien n…ôha kauvei pehe narimnari nepw…®n mwi mik. N…ôrim…®ru me n…ôha kauvani …ômwesi n…®pwranraha pam ia t…ôkure n…®fat…ô, m…®ne n…ôrim…®ru me n…ôha kavi n…®tenraha t…® noien …ôr…ôha, ik rer…®m r…®pka…°ien mh…ô t…® nir…ôha.‚Äù (In r…®ni n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha n…ôri au…ôr a m…ô nuvei penien narimnari me n…ôha m Kumwes…ôn ramesi pen n…ôfe Loa rani.)
\v 9 M…ôt…ô Kristo rani mwi m…ô, ‚ÄúKumwes…ôn, …ôt…ô ro, iou iakauvehe m…ô tako n…ôkwam.‚Äù Ia n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha s…ôv…ônhi ramousi raka n…ôkwai Kumwes…ôn s…ô kupw…ôn, m…ô in tr…ômri n…ôkwai Kumwes…ôn s…ô kurir…ô.
\v 10 \x - \xo 10:10 \xt Hip 9:12,28\x*N…ôn…ô n…ôkwai Kumwes…ôn s…ô n…ôha s…ô kurir…ô r…®naikuas raka noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôk…®taha n…ôp…®n Iesu Kristo r…®m…ôuvei pen n…®pwran m Kumwes…ôn m kuatia a, n…ôn…ô ko r…®pkuvei pen mh…ô mwi n…ôp…®n riti mwi.
