\v 3 \x - \xo 13:3 \xt Mat 25:36, Hip 10:34\x*Rer…®miaha tramrhi n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme hamar…ô ia kalapus r…ômwhen m…ô k…®miaha mwi hiamar…ô ia kalapus k…®miaha m…®nraha. Rer…®miaha tramrhi n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme n…ôrmama …ôp…ô me hamo ir…ôha h…ôre…°i r…ôr…ôha anan ia n…®pwranraha. Rer…®miaha tramrhi ir…ôha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô k…®miaha mwi hiamre…°i r…ôr…ôha ia n…®pwramiaha r…ômwhen ia nir…ôha.
